This is a list of skills to learn in React. These should be broken into small chunks for progressive learning 

1) Creating a React project
10) Removing default elements of a new React project so that it displays 'Hello World'
20) Create a main component that renders and returns a h1 title element
30) Create a child component and add it to main component
40) Create state in main component and pass down the child component
50) Create child class component & stateless functional component to compare
60) Utilise lifecycle hook